    section.section
      .section__in.features: .features__in
        .features__side
          .heading-title.text-red Features
        .features__main
          .feature
            .feature__main
              h3 Free
              div All source codes is published under GLP license. You are free to migrate from SaaS to your own installation at anytime.
            .feature__index 1
          .feature
            .feature__main
              h3 Flexible
              div You have freedom to design any decision rules on any data model, and to manage everything on the fly, without re-deploying stuff.
            .feature__index 2
          .feature
            .feature__main
              h3 Rich functionality
              div Define decision and scoring tables. Add variants to run split tests. Change allocation between them. Review and analyze all decisions. Debug tables in GUI. Share access with your collaborators.
            .feature__index 3
          .feature
            .feature__main
              h3 Simple to use and maintain
              div GUI is simple and intuitive. Docs are well-written. Code is covered with tests.
            .feature__index 4
          .feature
            .feature__main
              h3 Enterprise Ready
              div Several large PSP's and online lending platforms already use Gandalf. Join them!
            .feature__index 5
